# Build artefacts committed for runtime hermeticity:
#
#   dist/wake_word.bundle.js   ← committed (kiosk loads it)
#   dist/pcm-worklet.js        ← committed (AudioWorklet asset)
#   models/melspectrogram.onnx ← committed (auto-fetched, pinned)
#   models/embedding_model.onnx ← committed (auto-fetched, pinned)
#   models/silero_vad.onnx     ← committed (auto-fetched, pinned)
#   models/wake_word.onnx      ← committed when operator trains it
#   models/ort/*.wasm          ← committed (ONNX Runtime Web)
#
# Everything else npm produces is build-local clutter.
node_modules/
package-lock.json
.vite/
*.tsbuildinfo
.DS_Store
